deck: Handsome, young, smart and rich. Alex Poniatowski at the age of 31 won everything. He was president of Poland's largest corporation Tech Corp, had a beautiful wife.But fate had other plans for him . On the fateful day Alex does not remember anything. He mysteriously fell out of the office, and although he survived the fall he fell into a coma for three years. When all acquitted him already at a loss, he unexpectedly returned to the world of the living...
description:
Origin

Alex Poniatowski fell out of the building. He had no right to live. He broke not only most of the bones in his body but also a fundamental principle of life - escaped from the clutches of death. Four years later, thanks to a special serum returns as a superhero, White Eagle. He does not remember details of the accident, looking for their missing father, people who tried to kill him and ... his beloved wife. In the fight against the dangers which threaten Poland, corporation Techcorp, and his old friend Victor Ross, he is assisted by the young genius inventor - Hudini.

Unfortunately, the damage which he suffered were so severe that Alex woke up paralyzed. Dramatic attempt to restore his performance took on Alex's father Karol - scientist and the only person who never doubted him . However, during the treatment with an experimental serum, in the body of Alex occurred unforeseen changes.

Aleks got superpowers, so that increased his physical strength and gained an incredible resilience. Additionally, thanks to the latest technology and special giveaways he is able to fly and move with high speed.

Story

In the series first flight, White Eagle tries to explain the mystery that hides TechCorp. Alex to function effectively still needs serum which was created by his father. For this reason, he sneaks into the Tech Crop and steals the serum. However, it dispenses with it without a fight - facing him is Project Zero, which also uses the power of the serum.

Project Zero turns out to be too strong, Alex escapes, but his costume was seriously damaged and White Eagle falls under the train. When he wakes up discovers that he is in the sewers of Warsaw, where Nur -super villain wants to eat him. From oppression he was saved by the Wretched Polish Knight.

In subsequent issues White Eagle faces the challenge of saving Warsaw from total destruction that was caused by the conversation of Mr. Question and Mr. Answer. He got a help from two new super heroes Siren, and Project Zero - who escaped from Tech Corp.
name: White Eagle

deck: Young genius. Associate of the White Eagle.
description:
Origin & Story

Hudini we already know from the first pages of the book, when he helps to break up the White Eagle to TechCorp. This fashion genius often saved the skin of the White Eagle with the help of his knowledge and the computer, which practically he never parted. With it, he can break the security problems (eg TechCorpu) and help the White Eagle in saving the world (positioning, navigation, granting councils, the creation of gadgets the likes of "flying system", ie shoes with boosters with special ballasts.).

Hudini worked with Alex's father, Karol, on the hitherto unknown inventions yet. He also helps Karol Poniatowski to care his son after the explosion in the lab, and later in his mysterious disappearance.

The boy has quite a sense of humor, which often irritates the White Eagle.
name: Hudini

deck: Karol Poniatowski, a former scientist of Tech Corp, father of Alex Poniatowski. During his work in Tech Corp he worked on the application of new technologies in medicine.
description:
Origin & Story

Alex's father, he worked in TechCorp on the use of new technologies in medicine. After an accident of Alex and the TechCrop takeover by Victor Ross, he was fired from the company and its achievements and results of the work has benn taken over by the newly created Division of Military Technology. Karol Poniatowski first worked in the serum TechCorp increasing human strength.

Father of Alex, was with White Eagle at the time when when he was in a coma and never stopped believing in his return. Just as never come to terms with paralysis son, promising that he will fix it. He used the serum on Alex and after the experiment Alex gained super powers and become the White Eagle.

Karol Poniatowski seems to hide a lot of family secrets, before whom he tried to protect Alex. However, fate soon reassert its descendant

He disappeared after his house was visited by Victor Ross.
name: Karol Poniatowski

deck: Former friend of Alex, who along with him founded Tech Corp., currently the most powerful and influential corporation in Poland.
description:
Origin & Story

Former friend of Alex , who along with him founded TechCorp , now the most powerful and influential corporation in Poland.

The fate of Alex and Victor intertwined practically their whole life. Even as young boys they competed in science, in sport , girlfriends . But they were always remain loyal to each other - one could count on the other, even in the most difficult situations.

Success of TechCorp changed Victor and although it Alex became president, however Victor like staying in the shadows, seemed to be the person appealing for all the strings in the company. Victor at once more impressed power and influence, he began to become embroiled in shady deals with politicians and the underworld. He became ruthless and power-hungry.

His obsession became experimental serum, aimed at increasing the strength and resilience of man, thus creating a perfect super soldier manner.
name: Victor Ross

deck: Trusted assistant of Victor Ross, specializing in martial arts, a dangerous assassin. in and History of the Black Death remains unknown.
description:
Origin & Story

Trusted assistant Victor Ross, She specializes in martial arts, a dangerous assassin. In TechCorp appeared only after the accident Alex. He works directly for Victor.

Her nails give off a strong, paralyzing toxin that in large doses can lead to death. Origin and History of the Black Death remains unknown.

She fought with the monsters that have been recalled to Warsaw as a result of the conversation of Mr. Ask and Mr. answer. Her job was to collect genetic material from extraterrestrials and delivering them to TechCorp.

She also supervises research on the serum in the TechCorp company
name: Black Death

deck: Project Zero is the first Super Soldier prototype produced by TechCorp. It was created at the request of the Polish government after the terrorist attacks in Warsaw.
description:
Origin & Story

Super Soldier is a serum assisted soldier is twenty-first century. It is durable, extremely strong and equipped with an arsenal of modern weapons. Project Zero was under the control of its creators - TechCorp, passing a series of tests and experiments, which have to decide about his suitability for the military. Order the production of Super Soldiers can bring TechCorporation billions dollars.

After the fight with White Eagle in the First Flight his suit and body was very damaged. Victor Ross took him to the laboratory and start experiments again. After an exposition to the serum Project Zero recovered but also fell a strong pain because of the Serum. He regained also his consciousness that earlier inexplicably was blocked by the Black Death and after escaped from the laboratory.

Later he can be seen in the fight with White Eagle and Sirene, together they defend Warsaw from the big monster.

About a man who agreed to become the Project Zero and took part in the Super Soldier nothing is known, it is assumed that it was a volunteer whose motivation remains a mystery (TechCorp didnt reveal his personal details).
name: Project Zero

deck: Cannibal mutant living in the basement of the Central Station. One of main White Eagle oponent.
description:
Orgin & Story

Living in the basement of the Central Station, cannibal. His appearance arouses disgust, but it is unclear what caused him to these hideous body deformities.

Nur has the ability to control mind. He possessed many homeless people who faithfully serving him as dangerous and blindly devoted army. Nobody knows how he is able to control them and how to trigger this condition.

He is suspected of the disappearance of many people in the region of Central Station but the police never managed to fall on his trail. Officially denies its existence, all reports of Nur are treated as an urban myth.

Nur can be seen in the First Flight (series) where he captured White Eagle - after the main super hero escaped from the battle with Project Zero. He wanted to eat White Eagle. Later Nur was eventually defeated by the White Eagle, thanks to help from the Wretched Polish Knight. Since that time he didnt appeared in the White Eagle series.
name: Nur

deck: Wretched Polish Knight is one of the more mysterious allies of the White Eagle. This dressed in a blood red suit, with a huge, ragged cloak gentleman appears in different historical periods, to protect and defend our country from the dangers.
description:
Origin & Story

Wretched Polish Knight is one of the most mysterious allies of the White Eagle. This dressed in a blood red suit, with a huge, ragged cloak gentleman appears in different historical periods, to protect and defend our country from the dangers. In the story titled "First Flight" he played a significant role - he saved White Eagle in the fight against Nur and his mind controlled homeless, as well as Alex and Hudini, Knight led the team to a secret lab of Techcorp. Wretched Knight knows very well ancestors of White Eagle and is concealed by Poniatowski mystery, but does not reveal it to anyone, even to Alex.

It prefers melee weapons: long sword and shield are its hallmarks.
name: Wretched Polish Knight

deck: Wife of the White Eagle. She disappeared after the fatal accident of her husband Alex.
description:
Origin & Story

Wife of the White Eagle. Alex loves her more than anyone else in the world. Beautiful, young, intelligent, with impeccable manners. It simply created a woman for a man with the position of Alex. Their relationship seemed to be perfect.

Unfortunately, after the unlucky accident Alice disappeared without a trace - never appeared in the hospital when Alex was lying in a coma, or also when our hero woke up from it. It would seem that she had forgotten about him in a split second.

Alice is one of the main inspirations of the White Eagle, which does not stop in her quest. Very often thought about her and wondered why everything changed.

She is probably implicated in the "accident" with Alex.

deck: Dante was a resident of Des Plaines, Illinois until the Terrigen Mists appeared and turned him into the Inhuman, Inferno.
description:
Origin

Dante Pertuz was a musician living in Des Plaines, Illinois, when the Terrigen Mists appeared, and overtook him, transforming him into an Inhuman. Upon his transformation, Dante erupted in flames, accidentally torching his house and his mother. His pregnant sister, Gabriela, was his only family member to survive the experience, and traveled with Dante when Medusa and Gorgon arrived to bring him to New Attilan. Medusa used her prehensile hair to smother the flames on Dante's body, and Gorgon agreed to train him in the use of his powers.

Creation

Inferno was created by Charles Soule and Joe Madureira and first appeared in Inhuman issue 1 (2014).

Major Story Arcs

Out of the Darkness

Dante was present during an attack by three recently transformed Inhumans, like himself, (dubbed NuHumans) who opened fire on Queen Medusa in the bazaar outside of New Attilan. Thor was present and was speaking with the queen on the state of affairs in her newly established sovereign state. Dante ogled at Thor when Medusa introduced them, barely able to construct a coherent sentence. Medusa and Thor quickly rounded up the miscreants, and Medusa let them live, with an explanation that she would never force a NuHuman to remain on New Attilan, but she would always be there to help them. The NuHumans left, satisfied.

The Unspoken

Soon thereafter, the malevolent banished king of the Inhumans, known as the Unspoken, arrived in New Attilan with gifts in the form of three NuHumans, and asked for Medusa's hand in marriage, arguing that she was a kingless queen who could benefit from his ages of experience and his knowledge. Medusa immediately refused, knowing the Unspoken to be a cunning, manipulative liar. She accepted his gift of the NuHumans, and instructed Gorgon to place the Unspoken in a not-especially uncomfortable cell - which was exactly what the Unspoken wanted. With his knowledge of the city, he was able to open a secret passage from the cell down into a secret chamber in which the final store of Terrigen crystals was hidden away, unbeknownst to Medusa. The Inhuman Queen, cunning as she is, knew he would lead them there, and surprised the Unspoken in the chamber. However, the Unpoken's NuHumans attacked and distracted Medusa and Gorgon long enough for the Unspoken to reach the crystals, granting him youth, strength, and power. He incapacitated Medusa and Gorgon, and his forces began landing in the city. Dante, Flint, and Naja, who had been wandering about Manhattan, noticed that something had gone horribly wrong in the city. Naja flew both Flint and Dante over the Hudson River, into the city, and the three met up with the queen's chief medical officer, who led them to the Unspoken's makeshift throne room. The medical officer was immediately killed, fueling the fury of Dante's flames. Naja's chameleon-like abilities allowed her to get close to the Unspoken while Dante distracted him with his attack. Flint was able to destroy the crystals, leaving the Unspoken powerless. He was subsequently defeated by Naja.

Search for Black Bolt

Ennilux and Meeting Iso

Powers and Abilities

Pyrokinetic abilities

After undergoing the terrigenesis Inferno acquired several pyrokinetic powers.

  • Flame/Rock Form: Inferno has the ability to turn into a flame/rock form with will, though at the moment Inferno lacks control of this ability and sometimes burst into flames without his own will. He is normally immune to his own abilities, but sometimes if he loses control or uses too much his powers he can basically burn himself out.
  • Pyrokinesis: Inferno also has the ability to control the flames what his body generates but he can also create flames from thin air without turning into his flame form. Normally he uses this ability to shoot blast of fire concentrated plasma.
  • Regeneration: Inferno has unique ability to regenerate missing limbs (and presumably other wounds) from a unique fire plasma which his body generates. He has also many times burnt himself out and suffered from bad fire burns, but later seen to be completely healed.
  • ''Invulnerability'': Though he isn't invulnerable in common sense the intense heat which his body generates burns most attacks before harming him severally.
